The paper presents a method for autonomous MRI-guided ultrasound acquisitions using a robotic system, which involves computer vision techniques for patient-to-robot and image-to-patient calibration, as well as automatic MRI/US registration. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Medical Imaging (cs.MED), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
